          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "正要前去当面讲，\n昌黎曾祭又何妨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你是何处木鬼山魈，敢来俺镇上兴妖作怪？你如今若能降下一阵风雪，我信你\n是位正神。"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "神灵，这相公不信你的显应，你可速显威灵，步云降雨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公要的是风雪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要风雪么，这又何难！速降，降！吾奉太上老君急急如律勅。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（爰爰道人低声。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "黄袍爷爷，黄袍祖宗，黄袍老官，没有风雪，也弄阵子雨来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "妖怪，俺如今在此挺身，任你施为罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "快捆起狂生来，存些脸面，神圣爷爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你这道人，不是相公正气冲散，我们被你迷惑几时是了！列位，打这妖道！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众乡民打爰爰道人下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日这坛祭筵，亏得相公识出底细，竟然打散了。但不知什么爰爰道人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "列位不知，他取的名儿，却见于《诗经》上边。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么讲？"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "“有兔爰爰，雉离于罗”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若非相公指破群迷，我们怎得脱他罗网。请上，容我们拜谢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "闻仁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。列位将这庙宇，改为乡约所。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相公就是张道陵，能降妖怪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乡民甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是张道陵，倒是一位有识之士。张道陵降魔要符咒，相公降魔只动口。可不\n道："
        },
        {
          "character": "乡民甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宁动知识手，不动知识口。相公方动口，妖怪就出丑。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众乡民同笑。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众乡民",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是吓。相公请！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
