    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "爰爰道人",
        "黄袍大仙"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（爰爰道人跑上。黄袍大仙赶上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我正在作难，偏偏我的黄袍祖宗，你方才哪里去了？为何不似往日显圣了？弄\n我出这场大丑。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄袍大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大丑？你这小丑，你不知道往日显圣，只好吓那班村夫俗子。闻生是个正人，\n他乃文曲星降凡，魁光射斗，我怎么近得他？"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然如此，你方才出门时，吩咐我存些体面，你自己不顾脸面了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄袍大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我道行有限，脸面怎么顾得来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一场好事遭他贬，"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄袍大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你去请了白骨夫人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄袍大仙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "同我去宝象国法力施展。"
        },
        {
          "character": "爰爰道人",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住，近日出此大丑，闻生这口气，怎么出得？"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄袍大仙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你不要管，我自有处。"
        },
        {
          "character": "黄袍大仙",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只教他受屈难伸在后边。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（黄袍大仙、爰爰道人同下。）"
        }
      ],
